1. Create a new JavaScript project and add all system libraries to the include path
2. Copy the file qx.js from http://dev.eclipse.org/viewcvs/index.cgi/org.eclipse.rap/org.eclipse.rap.rwt/js/qx.js?root=Technology_Project&view=co into the script/ folder of the javascript project
3. Open the file qx.js and run the formatter on the file
4. Save
